# Venue POS — Core

## Read first
- Team setup: `docs/DEVELOPMENT.md`
- What's built: `docs/TEAM_LOG.md`
- Build spec: `.cursor/PROJECT_SPEC.md`
- User stories: `docs/PRD.md`

## Stack (do not swap)
Node 20 · Fastify · **Prisma 6** · PostgreSQL 16 · Redis · Socket.IO 4 · React 18 · Vite 5 · Tailwind 3 · Electron 30 · better-sqlite3 (local-agent) · Zod · bcrypt · JWT RS256

## Layers
| Layer | Path | Runtime |
|-------|------|---------|
| Server API | `apps/api` | Node + Postgres |
| Admin web | `apps/dashboard` | Browser |
| POS / KDS | `apps/pos`, `apps/kds` | Electron |
| Terminal service | `apps/local-agent` | Node + SQLite |
| Shared | `packages/shared`, `packages/i18n` | Imported by apps |

## Hard rules
- POS renderer → local-agent IPC only (no SQLite in Electron renderer)
- Offline-first: local write → sync queue → idempotent `syncId`
- Menu read-only on POS; publish from dashboard
- Bilingual UI via `@venue-pos/i18n`; DB fields `nameEn`/`nameAr` with `@map`
- No PAN storage; PINs never in API responses
- Prisma for all server DB access — no raw `pg` pool

## After every feature
Update `docs/TEAM_LOG.md` with date, author intent, files touched, and how to verify.
